videos.description: Ashton Hagans lobs it high to Nick Richards who finishes with nasty two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Richards skies for alley-oop finish

videos.description: Nick Richards is dominating early as he fights through contact and finishes a  tough layup for an and-1.
videos.headline: Richards finishes layup through contact for and-1

videos.description: Texas A&M cutting into Kentucky's lead as Josh Nebo gets up for a nice two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Nebo rises for two-handed flush

videos.description: Ashton Hagans drives past Texas A&M defenders and throws a sweet wrap-around pass to Reid Travis who slams it home.
videos.headline: Hagans' sweet dime leads to Travis' two-handed slam

videos.description: Ashton Hagans throws the ball in the air with 1.0 seconds on the clock, receiving a shot clock violation. Texas A&M's Savion Flagg then drains a 3-pointer as the buzzer sounds.
videos.headline: Kentucky's shot clock violation, Texas A&M's 3 is a bad beat
